@startuml
actor Nurse
participant "Mobile App UI" as UI
participant "Geoapify API" as Geo
participant "Distance Service" as Distance
participant "Database" as DB

Nurse -> UI : Enter postcode / Use location
UI -> Geo : Request coordinates/postcode
Geo --> UI : Location data

UI -> DB : Request services by category
DB --> UI : Service list

UI -> Distance : Calculate distances
Distance --> UI : Distances

Nurse -> UI : Confirm service
UI -> DB : Save patient record
DB --> UI : Confirmation success
@enduml
